We recommended that:
The City Inventory Committee complete the conduct of physical count of PPE so they could submit the complete Report on the Physical Count of Property, Plant and Equipment (RPCPPE) not later than January 31 of each year pursuant to Section 124 of the MNGAS for LGUs, Volume I;

